bio: Toshi Omagari is a Japanese type designer. He studied typography and type design at \
  Musashino Art University. After graduating in 2008, Toshi started teaching graphic design \
  at a local school in Fukuoka. Toshi will be studying type design further at the University \
  of Reading in the summer of 2010.
